  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Sextant</b> is an <linked>informational accessory</linked> that displays the current <linked>moon phase</linked>. It can be received as a <span class=\"chance\"><s>3.33*</s>1/30 (3.33%)</span>  chance reward for completing <linked>fishing</linked> quests for the <linked>Angler</linked> <linked>NPC</linked>. It is part of the <linked>Cell Phone</linked>'s crafting tree.",
    "The Angler will not give the player a Sextant as a reward if they already have one in their inventory or in any of their <linked>portable storage</linked>. However, if they have a <linked>Fisherman's Pocket Guide</linked>, <linked>Weather Radio</linked>, <b>and</b> Sextant (or at least one of the accessories crafted from them: the <linked>Fish Finder</linked>, <linked>PDA</linked>, or <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Cell Phone</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span>) in their inventories, he will be able to give them duplicate Sextants."
